      "text": "clinical_practice_guideline_chunks\n  id UUID  (UUID5: guideline_id:ver:i)\n  content TEXT\n  embedding vector(1536)\n  fts tsvector  (GIN)\n  content_hash TEXT  (SHA-256)\n  guideline_id TEXT\n  guideline_version TEXT\n  is_current_version BOOL\n  superseded_by TEXT\n  guideline_title TEXT\n  issuing_body TEXT\n  pub_year INT\n  evidence_tier INT\n  document_type TEXT\n  geographic_scope TEXT\n  source_url TEXT, licence TEXT\n  cascading_path TEXT[]\n  chunk_index INT, total_chunks INT\n  word_count INT\n  chunk_type TEXT DEFAULT 'text'\n  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ\n\nIndexes:\n  HNSW cosine (embedding)\n  GIN (fts)\n  B-tree is_current_version\n  B-tree (guideline_id, version)",
