      "originalText": "comments\n  id UUID PK\n  post_id UUID FK posts CASCADE\n  author_id UUID FK user_profiles CASCADE\n  parent_comment_id UUID FK self NULL\n    (NULL=top-level, non-NULL=reply)\n  content TEXT CHECK(length 1-2000)\n  is_anonymous BOOL DEFAULT FALSE\n  like_count INT DEFAULT 0\n  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ\n  is_deleted BOOL DEFAULT FALSE\n\nIndexes: (post_id, created_at),\n  parent_comment_id\nRLS: SELECT if not deleted, write own\nTrigger: update_post_comment_count()\n  AFTER INSERT -> comment_count++\n  AFTER DELETE -> comment_count--\n  on posts",
