      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "lib/api.ts\n  streamSearch()      async generator; parses raw SSE\n  REST helpers        conversations, posts, surveys\n\nlib/supabase.ts\n  createBrowserClient()  Supabase browser singleton\n  getAccessToken()       JWT from Supabase session\n\ntypes/index.ts\n  SSEEvent, Citation, ChatMessage\n  Conversation, Post, Comment\n  Survey, SurveyResponse, UserProfile\n  StreamingState\n\npage.tsx state machine\n  idle → loading → streaming → done\n  renumberByAppearance() — reorders citations\n  by first appearance in answer text",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "lib/api.ts\n  streamSearch()      async generator; parses raw SSE\n  REST helpers        conversations, posts, surveys\n\nlib/supabase.ts\n  createBrowserClient()  Supabase browser singleton\n  getAccessToken()       JWT from Supabase session\n\ntypes/index.ts\n  SSEEvent, Citation, ChatMessage\n  Conversation, Post, Comment\n  Survey, SurveyResponse, UserProfile\n  StreamingState\n\npage.tsx state machine\n  idle → loading → streaming → done\n  renumberByAppearance() — reorders citations\n  by first appearance in answer text",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b2B",
      "autoResize": true
    },
