    {
      "id": "mb_c5_txt",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2018,
      "y": 3824,
      "width": 598,
      "height": 558,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#334155",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 22676,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 1967066747,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777442117487,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "src/lib/\n  supabase.ts    AsyncStorage auth persistence\n  auth.ts        signUp / signIn / signOut / getUser\n  haptics.ts     tap / success / error / selection\n  motion.ts      tapDuration / transitionDuration consts\n  routing.ts     getPostAuthRoute(userId)\n  analytics.ts   PostHog event wrapper (dev-only)\n  deepLinks.ts   password-reset deep link handler\n\nsrc/hooks/\n  useFonts.ts    useQwivaFonts() — loads all 4 families\n  useShake.ts    shakeX Reanimated animation\n\napp.json\n  SDK 54  ·  newArchEnabled: false\n  scheme: qwiva  (deep links)\n  plugins: expo-router, expo-font\n\nKnown hard constraints\n  Reanimated 4.1.1 PINNED\n    SDK 54 bundles it natively;\n    downgrading → installTurboModule crash\n  New Arch disabled\n    required for TextInput focus stability\n  OTP paused\n    needs paid Supabase phone provider\n  package-lock.json FROZEN\n    npm install (no args) can re-resolve\n    Expo modules and break the build\n    Recovery: git checkout package-lock.json",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "src/lib/\n  supabase.ts    AsyncStorage auth persistence\n  auth.ts        signUp / signIn / signOut / getUser\n  haptics.ts     tap / success / error / selection\n  motion.ts      tapDuration / transitionDuration consts\n  routing.ts     getPostAuthRoute(userId)\n  analytics.ts   PostHog event wrapper (dev-only)\n  deepLinks.ts   password-reset deep link handler\n\nsrc/hooks/\n  useFonts.ts    useQwivaFonts() — loads all 4 families\n  useShake.ts    shakeX Reanimated animation\n\napp.json\n  SDK 54  ·  newArchEnabled: false\n  scheme: qwiva  (deep links)\n  plugins: expo-router, expo-font\n\nKnown hard constraints\n  Reanimated 4.1.1 PINNED\n    SDK 54 bundles it natively;\n    downgrading → installTurboModule crash\n  New Arch disabled\n    required for TextInput focus stability\n  OTP paused\n    needs paid Supabase phone provider\n  package-lock.json FROZEN\n    npm install (no args) can re-resolve\n    Expo modules and break the build\n    Recovery: git checkout package-lock.json",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b2c",
      "autoResize": true
    },
