      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777442117487,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "python -m evals.run_evals\n\nCLI flags\n  --skip-ragas\n  --skip-deepeval\n  --n N      run N questions\n  --report   output path\n\nFast mode (~1 min)\n  --skip-ragas --skip-deepeval\n  code metrics only\n  no LLM judge calls\n\nFull mode (LLM judge)\n  RAGAS + DeepEval\n  NVIDIA hub as judge\n  same model, zero extra cost",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "python -m evals.run_evals\n\nCLI flags\n  --skip-ragas\n  --skip-deepeval\n  --n N      run N questions\n  --report   output path\n\nFast mode (~1 min)\n  --skip-ragas --skip-deepeval\n  code metrics only\n  no LLM judge calls\n\nFull mode (LLM judge)\n  RAGAS + DeepEval\n  NVIDIA hub as judge\n  same model, zero extra cost",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b36",
      "autoResize": true
