      "text": "23 timestamped report pairs\n  YYYYMMDD_HHMMSS.json\n  YYYYMMDD_HHMMSS.md\n\nJSON structure\n  run_metadata\n    timestamp, model\n    n, skip flags\n  latency_percentiles\n  clinical_metrics\n  ragas_scores\n  deepeval_scores\n  per_question_results\n\nMarkdown report\n  Human-readable summary\n  Tables per metric\n  Per-question breakdown\n  Pass / fail vs thresholds",
